                     <interp inst="t18011202-14-verdict66" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder5s"></interp>
               Of stealing to the value of 3s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18011202-14-punish67" type="punishmentDescription">
